		"description": "{html}<div><p>Horizontal layout doesn't work on Android. It is very difficult\nto put labels next to each other without horizontal layout.</p>\n<p>For the following code the two labels are right on top of each\nother in the center of the view.<br></p>\n<pre>\n<code class=\n\"javascript\">var view= Ti.UI.createView({ width: 'auto', layout: 'horizontal' });\nview.add(Ti.UI.createLabel({ text: 'foo' }));\nview.add(Ti.UI.createLabel({ text: 'bar' }));</code>\n</pre></div>{html}",
